(2878, 1, '2013-09-24 09:48:13', '2013-09-24 09:48:13', 'The ability of sports to engage the audiences, young &amp; old alike, is unmatched by most other cultural elements. Besides, in a country where Cricket is not just a sport, but a religion, it is only logical that sporting events are the best way for the brands to connect with the audiences.\r\n\r\nCarat Fresh’s Sports Marketing team identifies the best opportunities for strategically associating your brand with the relevant sporting event, so as to ensure maximum visibility. 360 degree ROI based marketing plan is then devised to extend the reach beyond the boundaries of the stadium.\r\n\r\nSports Marketing Services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sports property associations</li>\r\n	<li>In-stadia/ out-of-stadia branding &amp; promotions</li>\r\n	<li>Innovative branding (off-air/ on-air)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Sports Marketing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2855-revision-4', '', '', '2013-09-24 09:48:13', '2013-09-24 09:48:13', '', 2855, 'http://localhost/caratfree/2855-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
